column5: I just found out I was off, anyone going pm me.Ill respond by 11pm.Doesnt matter where,the wife needs the truck and I need to get out of the house.Kitties in dunville or even bows in pr D.Doesnt matter, as long as im fishing.Cheers.
I'm in the Hammer, as you know, but I'll be working. And very, very jealous.  Make sure to bring the camera!
